WEBVTT

01:36.450 --> 01:37.780
What are you doing here?

01:42.280 --> 01:44.520
What? Is something there?

01:45.580 --> 01:49.490
If you're a Special Forces soldier,

01:49.490 --> 01:53.600
will they pick you up in a chopper? Would you be shot?

01:53.600 --> 01:56.780
South Korean soldiers would not get shot.

01:56.780 --> 01:58.950
They usually just get wet in the rain or snow.

01:58.950 --> 02:01.640
And they have to clean up themselves after that.

02:02.480 --> 02:03.450
Right?

02:05.660 --> 02:08.229
Then what about the man who flew away?

02:08.770 --> 02:12.420
Did someone fly away? Ran or flied away?

02:13.080 --> 02:15.210
Either way, they have to.

02:28.350 --> 02:30.480
Two UN workers active in the Gandamak region

02:30.480 --> 02:33.370
have been kidnapped by the Taliban.

02:33.370 --> 02:35.100
Next one, please.

02:35.100 --> 02:37.560
This is the building where the hostages are held.

02:37.560 --> 02:39.760
One team will enter from the northeast.

02:39.760 --> 02:42.430
The other will enter from the southeast.

02:46.720 --> 02:48.520
- Clear! - Clear!

02:48.520 --> 02:51.660
You have 90 seconds

02:51.660 --> 02:55.040
from entering to rescuing the hostages.

02:55.040 --> 02:56.100
Is that clear?

03:03.030 --> 03:03.790
No!

03:19.050 --> 03:21.370
Operation failed! We're all dead.

03:21.640 --> 03:24.600
It was a double booby trap. Pay your full attention!

03:24.600 --> 03:25.590
I'm sorry.

03:29.329 --> 03:31.110
Hey, man. What’s going on?!

03:31.110 --> 03:32.310
How about you

03:32.310 --> 03:34.579
and your Korean boy scouts go back home

03:34.579 --> 03:36.840
and train with your mamas?

03:41.030 --> 03:41.710
If you keep doing this,

03:41.710 --> 03:43.290
I will no longer restrain myself.

03:58.420 --> 04:01.020
-Pull him away. -Pull him away.

04:01.020 --> 04:06.420
-Yes, beat him. –Keep doing.

04:27.130 --> 04:28.930
If we don’t stop them, our captain may get killed.

04:29.990 --> 04:32.100
He could kill him or he could be killed.

04:34.070 --> 04:34.900
In a joint operation,

04:34.900 --> 04:37.210
Special Forces soldiers of first teamwork

04:37.210 --> 04:40.050
start a fight to see how good your partner is,

04:40.760 --> 04:41.950
in order to confirm during war

04:41.950 --> 04:44.950
if you can risk your life to your partner.

04:46.200 --> 04:48.740
They aren't sparring. This is for real.

04:49.020 --> 04:50.659
You can't interfere with them.

05:37.890 --> 05:39.070
Let go.

05:40.730 --> 05:42.860
Delta Force Captain, Blackbull!

05:42.860 --> 05:44.090
Yes, sir!

05:44.090 --> 05:46.480
707 Captain, Big Boss!

05:46.480 --> 05:47.260
Yes, sir!

05:47.260 --> 05:48.340
Break time’s over.

05:48.340 --> 05:49.870
Back to work now!

05:49.870 --> 05:51.980
Anyone got a problem?

05:53.990 --> 05:55.430
- No, sir! -No, sir!

05:56.720 --> 05:58.530
Last time I was the youngest applier,

05:58.530 --> 05:59.930
I knew nothing so I wasn't nervous.

05:59.930 --> 06:01.660
But I am so nervous this time.

06:01.660 --> 06:02.740
I don't remember any of the questions

06:02.740 --> 06:04.910
they asked. What should I do?

06:04.910 --> 06:06.560
Don't worry. You'll get it this time anyway.

06:06.560 --> 06:07.970
They won't fail you three times.

06:07.970 --> 06:10.970
Right? The director told me that

06:10.970 --> 06:13.700
my score was the highest in the information auditing.

06:21.190 --> 06:23.190
Wow! Doctor Kim! Do you have a date?

06:23.780 --> 06:26.590
I had an interview. After her.

06:28.260 --> 06:29.890
She…

06:32.360 --> 06:33.330
How did it go?

06:33.650 --> 06:34.950
They didn't ask you much, did they?

06:35.730 --> 06:36.880
Are you?

06:38.090 --> 06:41.010
They knew you wouldn’t understand anything.

06:41.510 --> 06:44.100
So they didn't have to ask questions.

06:45.130 --> 06:47.290
I have to go. I have surgery.

06:51.120 --> 06:53.090
Did she say the interview for the professor position?

06:53.780 --> 06:55.610
She even failed the specialist test three times.

06:55.610 --> 06:56.590
Four times.

06:57.770 --> 06:59.170
They may accept her application for increasing the numbers.

07:03.120 --> 07:04.140
Let's do this.

07:06.340 --> 07:08.140
You can't find your operating room?

07:08.730 --> 07:09.730
Professor Park is...

07:09.730 --> 07:11.580
The director changed his mind.

07:11.580 --> 07:15.310
I’ll do it for Professor Park. You're my assistant.

07:17.670 --> 07:18.730
What are you doing?

07:19.790 --> 07:22.560
Respiratory rate, 16. EKG is normal.

07:22.560 --> 07:24.690
Let's start. Scalpel.

07:30.550 --> 07:33.450
I heard that you helped Direction Park with his papers this time.

07:33.450 --> 07:35.110
You bought him a watch.

07:35.110 --> 07:36.940
Right-angled scissors.

07:38.159 --> 07:41.000
You work so hard in the discussion meeting. Try to win his support?

07:41.570 --> 07:43.720
The one who gave him a watch should win his support.

07:43.720 --> 07:45.630
I just want to be approved by my own ability.

07:50.140 --> 07:52.630
What are you doing? What did you touch?

08:18.510 --> 08:19.810
It's a tension pneumothorax.

08:19.810 --> 08:21.290
We have to help him decompress.

08:21.290 --> 08:22.260
14 gauge needle.

08:22.260 --> 08:23.860
I'm in charge here. I'll do it.

08:24.110 --> 08:25.300
Then do it quickly!

08:26.410 --> 08:28.580
Give me a 14 gauge needle.

08:35.460 --> 08:37.870
What are you doing? 28 French 10 TD.

08:37.870 --> 08:39.110
28 French…

08:59.020 --> 09:00.600
It's a trap! Get down!

09:54.050 --> 09:57.760
200 Joules! Charge!

10:10.090 --> 10:13.380
300 Joules! Charge!

11:26.550 --> 11:29.870
Mission complete! Hostages are safe.

11:36.750 --> 11:39.080
Blood pressure and pulse are normal.

11:40.120 --> 11:43.060
So lucky we pull it through.  You can finish it up.

11:45.370 --> 11:46.340
I will.

11:51.150 --> 11:52.830
If you're not good enough, practice more.

11:52.830 --> 11:53.550
If you're not smart enough,

11:53.550 --> 11:54.740
you should know it.

11:54.740 --> 11:57.050
Why does she insist to do it even if she’s not capable?

12:00.550 --> 12:02.610
I was so nervous earlier.

12:03.680 --> 12:05.710
You did great today.

12:06.600 --> 12:07.590
You did well.

12:14.210 --> 12:15.610
You too.

12:17.260 --> 12:18.970
By the way, what happened to your mom?

12:19.400 --> 12:20.560
Is she still a single mom?

12:20.560 --> 12:21.470
No!

12:23.650 --> 12:24.890
Look!

12:29.140 --> 12:30.300
Are you that happy?

12:31.580 --> 12:32.890
You two…

12:33.960 --> 12:34.980
Did he propose to you?

12:35.240 --> 12:37.700
Yes. We bought the rings first.

12:40.920 --> 12:42.420
Hi, sweetie!

12:44.920 --> 12:46.420
Hi, darling!

12:46.420 --> 12:47.840
How was the surgery?

12:49.150 --> 12:50.600
You’re so capricious!

12:51.900 --> 12:53.560
You said you needed

12:53.560 --> 12:54.660
to talk to me in private.

12:54.660 --> 12:55.840
What?

12:57.680 --> 13:00.550
Right. Can you excuse us?

13:01.030 --> 13:02.130
About what?

13:02.740 --> 13:04.270
A patient.

13:04.430 --> 13:08.200
Doctors should keep their information confidential.

13:08.200 --> 13:09.120
Yeah.

13:09.630 --> 13:12.310
Right. I'll see you later.

13:12.660 --> 13:13.460
See you later, sweetie.

13:13.460 --> 13:14.690
Sure, darling. See you.

13:20.980 --> 13:21.900
What now? What is it?

13:21.900 --> 13:23.370
I can't find my ring.

13:24.840 --> 13:25.910
Before I went into the OR this morning,

13:25.910 --> 13:26.950
I put it in my pants pocket.

13:26.950 --> 13:28.140
But it lost.

13:28.610 --> 13:30.760
You are so terrible, Lee Chi Hoon.

13:30.760 --> 13:31.270
I hope I didn't drop it

13:31.270 --> 13:32.810
in the patient's stomach.

13:32.810 --> 13:35.020
What? You crazy idiot!

13:35.020 --> 13:37.890
I found it. It was in my pocket of the surgery gown.

13:41.680 --> 13:44.580
Stand up. Clench your teeth.

13:53.150 --> 13:55.600
By the way, those two never leave the hospital.

13:55.600 --> 13:56.730
When did she get pregnant?

13:57.020 --> 13:58.540
This hospital is big.

13:59.600 --> 14:02.310
Stop. You're making me blush.

14:02.310 --> 14:03.930
Here. Ah…

14:10.590 --> 14:12.730
Did he call you?

14:13.100 --> 14:13.890
No.

14:16.200 --> 14:18.000
I don't think he's the kind of guy who calls often.

14:20.010 --> 14:21.370
Who is he?

14:22.170 --> 14:24.460
Soldier, gunshots, and a chopper...

14:25.670 --> 14:26.660
Is he a spy?

14:28.300 --> 14:29.250
Is he?

14:31.080 --> 14:31.860
What are you looking at?

14:33.480 --> 14:34.650
His picture.

14:37.300 --> 14:39.010
This is the only picture of him that I have.

14:41.810 --> 14:44.720
What an idiot!

14:57.320 --> 14:59.620
Have you eaten yet? I'm still clenching my teeth.

15:00.040 --> 15:00.940
You can unclench now.

15:01.340 --> 15:02.310
I'm off today.

15:02.310 --> 15:04.560
Don't text or call me from now on.

15:04.560 --> 15:05.680
I'm not going to answer it.

15:05.680 --> 15:06.790
What's going on?

15:07.860 --> 15:09.320
I have a date.

15:09.720 --> 15:11.000
You're not meeting him like that, aren’t you?

15:11.640 --> 15:12.840
You can’t do that!

15:34.040 --> 15:35.020
How are you?

15:38.450 --> 15:40.210
Why are you here so early?

15:40.210 --> 15:41.740
We still have

15:41.740 --> 15:42.820
two more hours to our date time.

15:42.820 --> 15:44.290
Am I wrong?

15:45.490 --> 15:47.000
I came early.

15:47.900 --> 15:51.000
It's a nice feeling to look forward to seeing someone.

15:51.680 --> 15:54.100
It's still not okay for you to come two hours earlier.

15:57.330 --> 16:00.290
Why are you avoiding my eyes?

16:00.290 --> 16:02.140
I feel a little insecure at the moment.

16:02.580 --> 16:04.160
I'm not wearing any makeup.

16:04.860 --> 16:07.480
I was going home to wash my hair and get changed.

16:09.370 --> 16:10.760
You're already pretty enough.

16:11.530 --> 16:12.640
Really?

16:13.540 --> 16:16.630
Why? Because I'm beautiful inside?

16:17.770 --> 16:19.440
If you can accept that, then I’ll quit.

16:19.580 --> 16:21.090
Get in. I drive you home.

16:22.230 --> 16:23.370
I guess you can’t.

16:33.240 --> 16:34.770
Come on in. It's clean.

16:35.180 --> 16:36.330
I don't have time to make a mess.

16:40.670 --> 16:42.290
I'll wash my hair quickly.

16:44.670 --> 16:46.940
By the way, I haven't eaten anything today.

16:46.940 --> 16:48.540
I’m so hungry now.

16:48.540 --> 16:50.880
How about we call a take out?

16:52.080 --> 16:53.990
I wanted to take you to a fancy restaurant.

16:54.960 --> 16:56.080
Are you okay with take-out food?

16:56.580 --> 16:57.420
I'm good because

16:57.420 --> 16:58.920
I have a cool guy to join me.

16:59.490 --> 17:02.150
The numbers are on the fridge. Please.

17:05.589 --> 17:06.619
What do you want?

17:06.619 --> 17:08.130
Iron pot bibimbap.

17:11.319 --> 17:12.319
She's very special

17:13.410 --> 17:14.400
and very pretty.

17:15.510 --> 17:18.270
Room 964. Thank you.

17:59.830 --> 18:02.490
What's this? Oh my god.

18:03.100 --> 18:05.350
Hey! What? No way!

18:06.710 --> 18:08.530
I'm not done washing up my hair.

18:10.790 --> 18:13.640
That feels good. I feel much better.

18:15.650 --> 18:16.710
Have you ordered food?

18:19.190 --> 18:20.030
Why are you looking at me like that?

18:20.490 --> 18:23.460
Did you finish washing your hair?

18:26.190 --> 18:27.890
The water was cut off at 4:00 p.m.

18:40.640 --> 18:42.270
It’s so cold. Shall I heat it uo for you?

18:42.270 --> 18:43.120
I'm fine.

18:55.030 --> 18:56.390
I want to ask…

18:56.390 --> 18:57.340
Don't.

18:58.310 --> 18:59.550
You know what my question is?

18:59.550 --> 19:02.280
I can see that you're going to make fun of me.

19:02.940 --> 19:05.910
How? It’s only a handsome look.

19:07.820 --> 19:09.060
What do you want to ask?

19:13.040 --> 19:14.150
Did you miss me?

19:15.450 --> 19:18.870
Of course. What about you?

19:21.150 --> 19:24.100
I missed you a lot. Like a man.

19:29.060 --> 19:30.590
Thank you

19:30.590 --> 19:32.030
for not making fun of me about my hair.

19:33.150 --> 19:34.490
Let's have coffee at the movies.

19:34.910 --> 19:35.810
Okay.

19:36.900 --> 19:39.830
I need to drink some water.

19:40.280 --> 19:41.260
Hey!

19:54.020 --> 19:55.450
Every time I come to the cinem,

19:55.450 --> 19:56.760
this is my favorite moment I feel the most excited.

19:57.320 --> 19:58.670
Just before the lights go out.

20:02.530 --> 20:04.340
This is my most excited moment

20:04.850 --> 20:08.580
that I'm with a beautiful lady before the lights go out.

20:09.630 --> 20:10.750
Not a senior citizen?

20:12.330 --> 20:14.270
The light is so dark.  I mistake you to be beautiful.

20:21.600 --> 20:24.460
You shouted at me earlier.

20:25.220 --> 20:26.570
So?

20:28.030 --> 20:29.080
How old are you?

20:29.800 --> 20:31.290
You already know my age from my history sheet.

20:31.780 --> 20:36.700
Well, you made fun of me first.

20:42.830 --> 20:44.070
So… I’m the older.

20:45.500 --> 20:47.960
I was joking. I'm older than you.

20:47.960 --> 20:49.310
I don't think so.

20:50.140 --> 20:51.300
Show me your ID card.

20:52.620 --> 20:54.190
I was worried that you might be a minor.

21:11.130 --> 21:12.050
Yes, sir.

21:13.510 --> 21:14.680
Captain Yoo Shi Jin.

21:16.180 --> 21:17.740
Yes, sir.

21:19.270 --> 21:20.430
Yes, sir.

21:21.170 --> 21:22.810
Understood.

21:24.700 --> 21:25.910
What's going on?

21:26.650 --> 21:27.770
I think I have to go now.

21:28.070 --> 21:28.930
Now?

21:29.460 --> 21:32.490
Yes. I'm sorry.

21:35.730 --> 21:37.570
Am I being stood up again?

21:40.720 --> 21:42.100
I'm so sorry.

21:42.380 --> 21:44.020
Let's watch this movie next time.

21:44.430 --> 21:45.350
We can leave here together.

21:45.350 --> 21:48.370
No. I'm going to finish. You can go.

21:49.640 --> 21:50.620
Why don't we watch it together?

21:50.620 --> 21:52.480
No, I'm good. You can go.

21:59.660 --> 22:00.550
I'll call you later.

22:14.890 --> 22:16.020
Mo Yeon, it's me.

22:16.600 --> 22:19.760
I wasn't going to bother you. But…

22:29.970 --> 22:30.800
Did you call her?

22:31.240 --> 22:32.230
How could I not?

22:33.200 --> 22:37.060
I thought Kang Mo Yeon would get the position.

22:37.060 --> 22:41.040
No one doubted that Kim Eun Ji would get the position this time.

22:42.340 --> 22:43.710
The previous two were her seniors,

22:43.940 --> 22:45.700
but Doctor Kim is in the same age with her.

22:46.640 --> 22:48.010
Kang Mo Yeon will be so mad.

22:49.140 --> 22:52.200
Dr.Kang has been nearly living in the OR

22:52.200 --> 22:53.960
That’s the reason why I think she’s so pathetic.

22:53.960 --> 22:55.280
She shouldn't have lived in the OR.

22:55.280 --> 22:56.880
She should be like the flowers in a greenhouse.

22:57.360 --> 22:58.950
I heard that Kim Eun Ji's father is a big

22:58.950 --> 23:00.710
shareholder of the Haesung Group.

23:00.710 --> 23:02.290
Kang Mo Yeon doesn’t.

23:02.290 --> 23:05.610
How can it be? You should judge a doctor by his ability.

23:05.610 --> 23:08.560
It doesn't matter how good you are.

23:08.560 --> 23:11.780
Doctors should be rich, and then physical.

23:11.780 --> 23:14.750
So you said they did it right?

23:15.330 --> 23:18.260
I'm not saying it's  acceptable…

23:18.700 --> 23:23.290
You said it'd be me. You promised.

23:23.990 --> 23:26.010
This is my third time.

23:26.010 --> 23:28.200
On my first try, you said I was too young.

23:28.200 --> 23:30.610
On my second try, you said you need to help

23:30.610 --> 23:32.140
those who helped you with your papers.

23:32.140 --> 23:33.900
How dare you!

23:33.900 --> 23:36.300
Do I owe you a professor position?

23:38.590 --> 23:40.870
If you said that, I have nothing else to say.

23:41.670 --> 23:44.540
Yes, I know family background is also a skill.

23:44.540 --> 23:46.010
Then who's next?

23:46.540 --> 23:49.350
A minister's son-in-law? Or the president's niece?

23:49.730 --> 23:52.280
After three tries, I thought there is at least one time

23:52.280 --> 23:54.090
I can depend on my professional skills.

23:54.930 --> 23:56.710
I thought you may not want a fourth chance,Dr.Kang

23:56.710 --> 23:57.830
Dr.Kang.

23:57.830 --> 23:59.100
Director.

24:02.410 --> 24:05.540
Professor Kim. We're done talking here.

24:05.540 --> 24:06.880
Give the materials of TV show

24:06.880 --> 24:08.250
to Dr.Kang,

24:08.250 --> 24:10.000
and come to Professor Park's office.

24:10.000 --> 24:12.410
We can all take his car.

24:12.730 --> 24:14.430
Yes, sir. I'll be right there.

24:15.050 --> 24:17.080
-Sir! -Hey!

24:18.620 --> 24:21.350
You have to be on the show for me tomorrow.

24:21.350 --> 24:23.440
I need to have dinner with my fellow professors.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.760
Are you asking me to fill in for you?

24:26.760 --> 24:30.350
Why not? You need to listen to

24:30.650 --> 24:31.720
what a professor ask.

24:31.720 --> 24:32.870
Don't make a fool out of yourself. It’s a live show.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.700
Learn this by heart.

24:35.120 --> 24:38.240
The hospital is paying lots of money for that show.

24:40.800 --> 24:42.020
What if I said I don't?

24:42.020 --> 24:44.320
Try it. You'll find out what happens.

24:44.820 --> 24:46.650
You're having dinner tonight. But your show is tomorrow.

24:46.650 --> 24:47.750
Why do I have to do it?

24:48.840 --> 24:52.370
Hey, I'm going to get drunk to celebrate becoming a professor.

24:52.370 --> 24:53.980
I don't think I can get up in the morning.

24:55.610 --> 24:57.010
You bitch.

24:57.500 --> 24:59.590
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

24:59.590 --> 25:01.490
Yes, I am.

25:01.490 --> 25:04.210
However, I got this professor position.

25:04.210 --> 25:06.570
You worked your butt off and what did you get?

25:08.080 --> 25:09.390
You bitch!

25:09.690 --> 25:10.860
- What? - You heard me.

25:10.860 --> 25:12.370
I said You're a bitch.

25:12.370 --> 25:14.640
I feel bad for your patients.

25:16.430 --> 25:17.410
Stop!

25:17.900 --> 25:19.720
So you're ashamed of yourself.

25:19.720 --> 25:21.580
That's making me more furious.

25:22.650 --> 25:24.850
- How dare you! - Let go! Let go!

25:24.850 --> 25:28.290
- You let go! - Let go!

25:28.290 --> 25:31.470
I'll do everything I can to stop you from becoming a professor.

25:31.470 --> 25:33.250
Are you crazy? Let go!

25:33.250 --> 25:34.500
- You let go first - Let go!

25:34.500 --> 25:35.790
Are you crazy?

25:36.380 --> 25:38.370
Let go off me.

25:38.690 --> 25:40.260
Hey, hey.

25:40.570 --> 25:43.250
What are you two doing?

25:43.730 --> 25:44.760
Let go! Both of you!

25:49.050 --> 25:50.610
What have I done?

25:51.440 --> 25:52.380
I must be crazy.

25:58.880 --> 26:02.130
For a patient with arrhythmia...

26:10.370 --> 26:13.510
For a patient with arrhythmia…

26:13.510 --> 26:16.840
A 12 lead EKG should…

26:17.180 --> 26:19.730
Why can't I remember?

26:25.290 --> 26:29.920
For a patient with arrhythmia...

26:41.100 --> 26:43.690
For a patient with arrhythmia,

26:43.690 --> 26:46.010
a 12 lead EKG…

26:49.050 --> 26:49.830
Good job, everyone!

26:49.830 --> 26:51.350
Thank you, sir! –Thank you.

26:51.430 --> 26:53.340
Until roll call, check your weapons thoroughly.

26:53.340 --> 26:54.960
- Yes, sir! - Yes, sir!

26:58.680 --> 27:00.470
- Attention! - At ease!

27:00.470 --> 27:01.300
At ease!

27:01.300 --> 27:03.290
All of you, at ease.

27:03.290 --> 27:04.680
Thank you for filling in for Bravo Team.

27:04.680 --> 27:05.960
Good job.

27:08.070 --> 27:09.510
Was anyone hurt?

27:10.080 --> 27:12.670
No, sir. No one was injured.

27:13.630 --> 27:14.360
Thank you.

27:16.530 --> 27:17.540
Alpha Team

27:17.540 --> 27:20.320
work hard in the operation at home and abroad.

27:20.720 --> 27:22.580
So as your commanding officer,

27:22.720 --> 27:25.180
I have decided to send Alpha Team

27:25.180 --> 27:26.780
on an eight-month long vacation.

27:31.670 --> 27:33.290
To where, sir?

27:33.750 --> 27:35.220
To Uruk where Taebaek Unit is stationed.

27:35.860 --> 27:37.390
For two weeks before training,

27:37.390 --> 27:39.890
you can visit your girlfriends and families.

27:43.770 --> 27:46.940
Get out of here as soon as possible. Dismissed.

27:48.370 --> 27:49.650
Yes, sir!

27:53.540 --> 27:56.430
Why are we getting a vacation for eight months?

27:56.430 --> 27:59.340
We're being dispatched. That's our vacation.

27:59.410 --> 28:00.900
We'll support the regular troops.

28:00.900 --> 28:01.590
Maybe we won't encounter any emergency fights.

28:01.590 --> 28:02.760
Then we can take a rest there.

28:05.840 --> 28:06.780
Yes.

28:06.780 --> 28:07.970
Bravos.

28:18.520 --> 28:21.560
Is Dr.Kang Mo Yeon in the OR at the moment?

28:22.590 --> 28:23.870
She didn’t answer her phone.

28:23.870 --> 28:26.670
Dr.Kang's right there.

28:27.170 --> 28:29.350
It's a live show.

28:29.730 --> 28:31.600
There are different types.

28:31.600 --> 28:33.770
When you get older, the odds increase.

28:34.540 --> 28:36.150
How do you treat a patient with arrhythmia?

28:36.150 --> 28:38.530
When we treat a patient with arrhythmia,

28:38.530 --> 28:41.000
we have a new EPS test

28:41.000 --> 28:44.610
and a new way of diagnosing

28:44.610 --> 28:46.480
that can minimize the side effects.

28:46.480 --> 28:47.430
I see.

28:47.430 --> 28:49.120
I heard this was your first time on a show.

28:49.120 --> 28:50.530
You don't seem to be nervous at all.

28:50.530 --> 28:52.770
Your explanations are really easy to follow as well.

28:53.140 --> 28:54.370
I'm shaking like crazy. I

28:54.370 --> 28:55.780
guess it doesn't show.

29:33.170 --> 29:38.520
I'm sorry that I left you alone that day.

29:40.650 --> 29:45.160
I don't want an apology but explanation.

29:46.850 --> 29:48.620
Where did you go this time?

29:49.830 --> 29:51.280
Went ti take a chopperagain?

29:52.650 --> 29:55.570
No. I didn't go far this time.

29:57.950 --> 29:59.630
Because of regulations,

29:59.630 --> 30:01.510
I can't tell you the details.

30:02.440 --> 30:04.020
Right.

30:04.780 --> 30:06.130
You're not a spy, are you?

30:14.380 --> 30:21.210
I had a very long day though, I thought about you now and then.

30:23.470 --> 30:26.280
The guy dated with me.

30:27.350 --> 30:28.980
What does he do?

30:31.880 --> 30:33.300
Now I'm with you,

30:33.750 --> 30:38.050
but you said you can't tell me

30:38.440 --> 30:39.690
because of regulations.

30:43.690 --> 30:45.140
I'm sorry.

30:45.560 --> 30:48.720
Are you with the Special Forces or something?

30:49.160 --> 30:50.120
Something like that.

30:50.120 --> 30:53.050
You said you shovel.

30:55.240 --> 30:57.230
But actually you have a gunshot wound,

30:57.230 --> 30:59.080
which means you've been shot.

30:59.910 --> 31:04.330
and that you can use a gun.

31:06.300 --> 31:07.780
So…

31:09.230 --> 31:13.630
You may kill or be killed.

31:15.080 --> 31:18.790
Is that what you do?

31:22.950 --> 31:25.100
Do you only deal with bad guys?

31:32.320 --> 31:33.920
I spend over 12 hours

31:33.920 --> 31:35.700
in the OR every day

31:35.700 --> 31:39.080
to save people who're about to die.

31:40.410 --> 31:44.220
That's what I do. I fight to save lives.

31:45.980 --> 31:48.500
But your fight

31:49.240 --> 31:53.640
is to save people by killing others.

32:02.820 --> 32:04.320
I'm a soldier.

32:05.870 --> 32:09.650
Soldiers need to follow orders.

32:14.540 --> 32:17.150
Even though what I believe

32:18.610 --> 32:19.350
might not receive

32:19.350 --> 32:20.480
the support of others,

32:23.040 --> 32:25.670
I will try my best to complete my mission.

32:29.720 --> 32:31.510
Till now

32:34.430 --> 32:36.900
I've lost three of my fellow soldiers.

32:41.460 --> 32:44.520
But someone needs to do these things.

32:44.520 --> 32:47.830
So I will continue to do this job.

32:47.830 --> 32:49.370
Me and my families,

32:49.370 --> 32:51.090
you and you families,

32:52.510 --> 32:54.370
and those important to our families.

32:58.850 --> 33:01.840
I believe my job will

33:01.840 --> 33:05.050
protect the freedom and peace in this country.

33:10.230 --> 33:11.990
I'm a doctor.

33:12.950 --> 33:14.820
I believe in the dignity of life

33:15.310 --> 33:18.520
and there's no value or ideology that surpasses that.

33:23.950 --> 33:25.440
Right.

33:31.820 --> 33:33.100
I'm sorry...

33:35.460 --> 33:38.130
But this isn't what I expected.

33:41.360 --> 33:42.540
I understand.

33:43.390 --> 33:45.030
I have to go.

33:45.450 --> 33:46.780
Nice meeting you.

33:51.730 --> 33:52.790
Take care.

34:42.989 --> 34:44.540
You came back early.

34:44.540 --> 34:46.540
Why are you here?

34:47.010 --> 34:48.880
You're not going to see Myung Joo before you leave?

34:49.760 --> 34:50.520
You won't be able to see her

34:50.520 --> 34:51.949
for over six months.

34:53.409 --> 34:55.090
Did you see that doctor?

34:56.600 --> 34:58.100
Pass me the razor.

35:04.800 --> 35:08.960
I heard that there are lots of pretty girls in Uruk.

35:09.360 --> 35:13.750
Kim Tae Hee in the rice field. Sistar members in the vineyard.

35:38.700 --> 35:41.350
I’m a real man

35:41.350 --> 35:42.390
-Handsome man –Handsome

35:42.390 --> 35:44.250
-I'm a real man -I'm an awesome man

35:44.250 --> 35:49.660
Left! Left! One, two!

36:23.130 --> 36:24.220
Are you taking a nap?

36:25.100 --> 36:30.080
I was thinking about our duty of keeping peace as soldiers.

36:32.140 --> 36:33.660
Would you like some iced coffee?

36:35.790 --> 36:37.420
I prefer mineral water.

36:39.430 --> 36:41.210
This is Piccolo. An unidentified

36:41.210 --> 36:42.370
explosive was detected on the B4 Line.

36:42.370 --> 36:43.690
An unidentified explosive was detected.

36:43.690 --> 36:46.210
It's an 82mm high explosive.

36:46.210 --> 36:47.910
It looks like it was used by Russia

36:47.910 --> 36:48.980
during the Sino-Soviet border conflict.

36:48.980 --> 36:50.820
The fuse is still intact.

36:50.820 --> 36:53.930
The kill radius is pretty high. We have to be careful.

36:56.930 --> 36:58.270
I've finished the basic process.

36:58.900 --> 37:00.040
What should I do with it?

37:00.430 --> 37:02.110
If we report it to the commander,

37:02.110 --> 37:03.510
he'll tell us not to touch it

37:03.510 --> 37:05.240
and to get cooperation from the US army.

37:06.860 --> 37:10.780
Sergeant Choi Woo Geun, what's my motto?

37:12.740 --> 37:15.320
Easygoing, carefree, a

37:15.320 --> 37:17.730
nd no headaches.

37:18.310 --> 37:22.060
Sergeant Im Kwang Nam. What causes headaches?

37:22.060 --> 37:23.920
First, letters asking for cooperation!

37:23.920 --> 37:25.170
Second, letters asking for cooperation!

37:25.170 --> 37:26.120
Third, letters asking for cooperation!

37:26.120 --> 37:27.200
The end.

37:28.730 --> 37:30.160
Let the US Army protect the earth.

37:30.160 --> 37:31.230
Don't bother them.

37:31.230 --> 37:33.600
We'll take care of this.

37:34.120 --> 37:39.400
I, the commanding officer, will take full responsibility.

37:41.060 --> 37:43.660
Who is it? Who did this?

37:46.180 --> 37:48.320
Just because you're on your own far away from headquarters,

37:48.320 --> 37:51.080
do you think you can just ignore your superiors?

37:51.440 --> 37:52.340
I’ve told you to manage blind shells only

37:52.340 --> 37:54.520
and to let the US EOD take care of

37:54.520 --> 37:55.820
explosives with still-intact fuses.

37:55.820 --> 37:57.090
Who was it?

37:57.560 --> 38:01.510
Who the heck is responsible for this?

38:02.720 --> 38:04.440
As far as I remember, my deputy

38:05.740 --> 38:06.820
didn't stop me.

38:08.200 --> 38:09.640
Why didn't you stop me?

38:09.640 --> 38:11.370
What’re you doing?

38:12.030 --> 38:13.650
You know how much I love writing

38:13.650 --> 38:15.860
letters asking for cooperation. How could you…

38:20.360 --> 38:22.690
I thought he has finished the letter asking for cooperation.

38:22.690 --> 38:25.520
Because... because...

38:26.130 --> 38:27.730
He's an eloquent writer.

38:28.620 --> 38:30.670
He's like Tolstoy

38:30.670 --> 38:32.900
when it comes to writing letters.

38:35.560 --> 38:39.010
You idiots. Both of you pack up your kits!

38:47.670 --> 38:49.550
They're here! They're here!

38:55.410 --> 38:58.940
Attention. Go!

39:01.300 --> 39:03.750
- Keep up the good work! - Keep up the good work!

39:13.130 --> 39:16.620
Don't you think physical punishment is better than writing a letter?

39:17.340 --> 39:19.040
Do you really want to the punishment?

39:33.160 --> 39:35.930
She's  elegant as usual.

39:36.250 --> 39:38.280
The best way to prevent it

39:38.280 --> 39:39.870
is with regular checkups, right?

39:39.870 --> 39:41.330
Yes.

39:41.330 --> 39:43.140
There's this carotid ultrasound

39:43.140 --> 39:46.030
in the health checkup program...

39:57.160 --> 40:00.280
Chairman Choi of the Seongjin Group took food today,

40:00.280 --> 40:01.660
and he felt much better.

40:01.660 --> 40:04.320
The wife of the Yoo Seong Electronics’ CEO is hospitalized again.

40:04.320 --> 40:06.130
She's back? Why?

40:06.130 --> 40:07.260
She just left yesterday.

40:07.260 --> 40:09.540
The CEO's legal wife came back and kicked her out.

40:09.540 --> 40:10.960
What?

40:10.960 --> 40:14.450
Those people mistake our hospital as hotels.

40:15.170 --> 40:17.960
Let's go and see our VIP patients.

40:17.960 --> 40:18.780
Yes.

40:18.780 --> 40:21.270
The patent-related lawsuits

40:21.270 --> 40:23.800
our company is involved in are so stressful.

40:23.800 --> 40:25.930
Something’s wrong with my body.

40:26.370 --> 40:28.070
Out of all the problems,

40:29.890 --> 40:33.540
this is most urgent. My new girlfriend…

40:33.540 --> 40:34.230
I don’t know if

40:34.230 --> 40:36.860
it’s because she’s so young. I felt so laborious

40:36.860 --> 40:38.670
Why don't you date an older woman then?

40:39.340 --> 40:40.820
Why would I waste money on an old women?

40:42.660 --> 40:44.090
Did you get the results?

40:44.090 --> 40:45.270
Ah, yes.

40:47.580 --> 40:49.340
He's your biological grandson, sir.

40:51.050 --> 40:52.370
Right.

40:53.340 --> 40:57.450
Well… Can you test this as well?

41:04.550 --> 41:06.210
Turkey ham and seafood sandwich

41:06.210 --> 41:09.130
to go, please.

41:09.130 --> 41:11.050
And one more chocolate chip cookies.

41:11.420 --> 41:12.910
Any vegetables you don’t like?

41:12.910 --> 41:14.130
No. All vegetables, please.

41:14.130 --> 41:16.010
With honey oat bread.

41:16.010 --> 41:17.440
By the way,

41:17.440 --> 41:19.370
you look prettier in person than on TV.

41:20.520 --> 41:21.810
Do you want me to heat up the bread?

41:21.810 --> 41:23.450
Yes, please. Thank you.

41:24.340 --> 41:27.770
Look who's here!

41:27.770 --> 41:29.070
Isn't it Professor Kang Mo Yeon,

41:29.070 --> 41:30.800
who's working in the Emergency Room

41:30.800 --> 41:33.520
and seldom appear here in public ward?

41:35.170 --> 41:36.820
Because of me, your workload is heavier.

41:36.820 --> 41:38.100
This is a bribe.

41:38.740 --> 41:40.570
I put olives for you.

41:40.570 --> 41:42.020
Thank you.

41:43.620 --> 41:45.660
You never know with life.

41:45.660 --> 41:46.770
When you were working your butt off in the OR,

41:46.770 --> 41:48.510
your life wasn't going well.

41:48.510 --> 41:50.140
After you drop down your scalpel and put up maicrophone,

41:50.140 --> 41:51.550
you're the face of Haesung Hospital

41:51.550 --> 41:53.720
and a professor taking care of VIPs.

41:53.720 --> 41:54.930
A ham sandwich for me.

41:55.510 --> 41:57.260
I can't get my head around it either.

41:57.260 --> 42:01.260
We never know how our life gonna change.

42:06.880 --> 42:10.290
By the way, on the show's message board,

42:10.620 --> 42:14.110
people said you're even more beautiful than the female host,

42:14.110 --> 42:15.190
Did you write them?

42:15.910 --> 42:17.380
I didn't.

42:17.380 --> 42:18.920
If you didn't write them,

42:18.920 --> 42:20.970
you're not curious who did this?

42:20.970 --> 42:24.120
His nickname is Doc. Song.

42:25.070 --> 42:26.480
Doc. Song?

42:27.910 --> 42:30.520
Right! Doctor. Song.

42:30.940 --> 42:34.400
Did you write them?

42:34.400 --> 42:36.810
Have some more.

42:38.270 --> 42:41.030
Unbelievable! Shame on you!

42:41.600 --> 42:44.280
You still introduce yourself as a surgeon.

42:49.600 --> 42:50.530
What are you looking at?

42:50.530 --> 42:51.780
I'm looking at you.

42:52.090 --> 42:53.220
You're not a surgeon either.

42:53.580 --> 42:55.150
You're just your father's daughter.

42:57.190 --> 42:59.410
A surgeon should be in the OR,

42:59.410 --> 43:00.670
not a dressing room.

43:00.670 --> 43:02.960
Neither you nor I are in the OR.

43:02.960 --> 43:04.860
I'm busy and you're not good enough.

43:04.860 --> 43:07.630
Don’t be aggressive. You can be on the show

43:07.630 --> 43:08.510
due to being my sustitue.

43:08.510 --> 43:11.360
Stop being jealous. You got fired when I showed up.

43:11.360 --> 43:13.320
You think you're a big shot, huh?

43:13.320 --> 43:14.710
You think you own the entire world?

43:15.340 --> 43:17.790
How can I own the entire world when it's so big?

43:17.790 --> 43:20.910
I just took back what was mine after you stole it from me.

43:20.910 --> 43:22.870
Why don't you leave me alone

43:22.870 --> 43:24.060
and focus on your life?

43:24.950 --> 43:27.460
-I have to go. -Bye.

43:28.520 --> 43:29.860
Hey! Hey!

43:31.080 --> 43:32.400
So annoying.

43:49.500 --> 43:50.930
I'll come back in full health.

43:51.970 --> 43:53.870
Let's go to a movie together.

43:55.350 --> 43:57.580
Quick! I have no time.

43:58.280 --> 43:59.400
Yes or no?

44:02.050 --> 44:03.250
Did you miss me?

44:04.600 --> 44:07.470
Of course. What about you?

44:07.470 --> 44:10.540
I missed you a lot. Like a man.

44:13.540 --> 44:14.890
This is our first date.

44:14.890 --> 44:16.270
I want to set the mood.

44:16.270 --> 44:17.350
I'll put it here.

44:17.350 --> 44:18.680
Why don’t put it in the middle?

44:20.210 --> 44:22.200
Women always need back light.

44:22.200 --> 44:24.920
I want the light behind me to make me look prettier..

44:24.920 --> 44:26.410
Don't move.

44:26.410 --> 44:29.200
I calculated the angle of your sight line as well.

44:33.300 --> 44:35.550
By the way, you're injured again.

44:36.240 --> 44:38.330
Was it shoveling again?

44:42.980 --> 44:46.420
What do you think the odds are that you'd hurt your face while shoveling?

44:47.350 --> 44:48.730
I didn't think so. Right?

44:48.730 --> 44:50.450
I was able to pull it off.

44:59.170 --> 45:02.600
You're too busy to wash your hair?

45:03.450 --> 45:05.740
I practically live in the OR.

45:06.950 --> 45:09.980
Do you know how sexy I am in the OR?

45:11.220 --> 45:13.060
Even if you see me like that,

45:13.060 --> 45:14.780
I'm still really pretty.

45:17.640 --> 45:19.640
I want to go out with that person.

45:20.430 --> 45:21.940
Where is she now?

45:22.240 --> 45:23.630
Hey.

45:35.600 --> 45:37.590
I haven't had a chance to be sexy lately.

45:47.340 --> 45:48.300
What are you doing?

45:49.430 --> 45:52.670
Sir! I’m Kim Ki Bum!

45:52.670 --> 45:54.170
I'm digging a drainage ditch.

45:54.170 --> 45:55.720
That's not what I'm asking.

46:00.210 --> 46:01.310
Give it to me!

46:06.020 --> 46:08.380
If you dig like that, you won't get anywhere.

46:08.800 --> 46:09.640
Look!

46:10.590 --> 46:13.760
Hold it here and use your shoulders and lower back.

46:13.760 --> 46:15.920
Like this…

46:19.560 --> 46:21.770
I was being careful not to hurt myself.

46:22.480 --> 46:24.350
Oh! You're bleeding.

46:24.750 --> 46:27.200
Geez. I actually got hurt while shoveling.

46:27.200 --> 46:28.280
Stay still.

46:28.280 --> 46:30.490
You need to get treated.

46:32.910 --> 46:34.340
Look at this…

46:36.370 --> 46:40.570
Attention! At ease!

46:40.570 --> 46:42.030
Attention!

46:42.330 --> 46:43.670
What's going on?

46:43.670 --> 46:44.480
Why did you bring this idiot with you?

46:44.480 --> 46:46.470
To a country far, far away?

46:46.470 --> 46:47.750
I find him adorable.

46:48.680 --> 46:49.890
What do you need? Just say that.

46:49.890 --> 46:52.210
I need some wine and fresh cream.

46:52.210 --> 46:52.930
Today's Staff Sergeant Gong's birthday

46:52.930 --> 46:54.560
and he wants to cook steak.

46:54.560 --> 46:56.270
He is an excellent cook.

46:56.660 --> 46:58.790
Right. It's his birthday today.

47:01.120 --> 47:04.920
You’re in charge of supplying wine. I’ll cover you.

47:11.350 --> 47:14.050
I'm getting whipped cream ready. Just wait a bit.

47:14.050 --> 47:16.180
- Yeah, no problem. - Sure thing.

47:21.620 --> 47:22.840
This is why I come here.

47:22.840 --> 47:24.220
She winked at me.

47:24.570 --> 47:26.320
Don't flatter yourself.

47:32.230 --> 47:34.420
Did you get what I asked you?

47:37.770 --> 47:39.660
Treat it with care. Girl.

47:42.020 --> 47:44.740
It's quite heavy. How do you use it?

47:51.450 --> 47:54.070
Are you scared? It works.

48:02.530 --> 48:03.380
Korean?

48:03.380 --> 48:05.160
I speak Korean, but it doesn't mean I'm Korea

48:08.350 --> 48:09.740
Give it to me! That's mine!

48:11.680 --> 48:14.090
A gun isn't a dog who knows its owner.

48:14.090 --> 48:15.880
This gun can hurt anyone.

48:21.550 --> 48:23.650
Why did you buy a gun you can't even handle?

48:23.650 --> 48:25.520
I didn't buy it to kill people.

48:27.270 --> 48:28.660
I bought it to protect myself

48:32.030 --> 48:33.220
What a snob!

48:38.020 --> 48:39.880
Can we let her take the gun?

48:40.500 --> 48:42.120
It's not illegal to own a gun here.

48:43.550 --> 48:48.470
Who was that? Not a tourist. A new face?

48:48.470 --> 48:50.720
There are two things that we don't sell here.

48:50.720 --> 48:53.090
Women and information.

48:53.090 --> 48:54.390
There's your whipped cream.

48:55.940 --> 48:58.990
Uruk? Where is Uruk?

48:58.990 --> 48:59.860
It's at the end of the Balkan Peninsula.

48:59.860 --> 49:01.120
At the west.

49:01.120 --> 49:02.610
Did Haesung Group build

49:02.610 --> 49:04.980
an environmentally friendly power plant there?

49:04.980 --> 49:06.610
They said it's volunteer work.

49:06.610 --> 49:07.560
No idea who will be assigned there.

49:07.560 --> 49:10.230
It must be someone hasno money and no strings to pull.

49:10.890 --> 49:12.430
That's me.

49:12.430 --> 49:13.690
I have no money, no strings to pull, and no luck.

49:13.690 --> 49:15.470
This is crazy.

49:15.470 --> 49:16.990
You're warmhearted

49:16.990 --> 49:18.260
and good-looking.

49:20.970 --> 49:22.330
Really? Am I?

49:23.700 --> 49:26.000
I'll join the medical services team.

49:26.000 --> 49:27.670
Doctor Jang said I could go.

49:27.670 --> 49:28.960
Stop.

49:28.960 --> 49:31.300
She's having a baby soon. You can't go.

49:31.300 --> 49:34.630
If she loves you, she won't let you go.

49:34.630 --> 49:36.870
She said this would be my last chance before our baby is born.

49:36.870 --> 49:37.950
So she asked me to go first.

49:38.120 --> 49:39.050
Geez.

49:39.050 --> 49:41.760
Why did a rich boy like you are so diligent?

49:41.760 --> 49:44.050
You should've lived like Bill Gates.

49:44.050 --> 49:45.400
Professor Kang.

49:51.380 --> 49:52.620
Make your time tonight

49:53.500 --> 49:55.170
to have dinner with me.

50:01.350 --> 50:02.790
Did the Mr.Han of our hospital

50:02.790 --> 50:04.830
just ask me out?

50:05.520 --> 50:08.540
- Oh my! - I know. Oh my god.

50:10.910 --> 50:13.370
What does rising star Kang Mo Yeon need the most at the moment?

50:13.370 --> 50:16.000
- A fan club? - Please. A political marriage.

50:16.310 --> 50:18.420
A political marriage!

50:19.350 --> 50:21.260
I feel like an important person.

50:21.260 --> 50:23.430
No way!

50:23.830 --> 50:25.790
He's been divorced once.

50:26.850 --> 50:28.140
Then doesn’t Dr.Kang waste her life?

50:28.180 --> 50:29.880
What are you talking about?

50:30.280 --> 50:32.150
Is she young? Are her parents rich?

50:32.480 --> 50:34.600
For someone who doesn't have a rich family,

50:34.600 --> 50:36.630
a divorce man is of her benefits.

50:36.630 --> 50:37.670
Right?

50:38.610 --> 50:42.320
Should I move up in social class?

50:50.100 --> 50:51.150
What are you doing? Have a seat.

50:53.680 --> 50:55.750
Are we having dinner here?

50:59.860 --> 51:00.450
You think we’re here

51:00.450 --> 51:01.720
only for the dinner?

51:02.130 --> 51:04.290
You said we were going to the Sky Lounge.

51:04.290 --> 51:08.700
Sky. Lounge. Here it is.

51:08.700 --> 51:09.840
What else do you need?

51:12.800 --> 51:17.730
Good manners? And I may be foolish to expect it from you,

51:18.090 --> 51:19.490
but romance?

51:20.280 --> 51:23.390
Are you the romantic type?

51:23.720 --> 51:25.980
You know I'm very direct and impatient.

51:27.020 --> 51:27.970
We can order dinner.

51:27.970 --> 51:30.390
Until food gets here, why don't you have a shower?

51:31.810 --> 51:33.000
Or do you want me to go first?

51:42.960 --> 51:45.520
That's better. Come on.

51:51.810 --> 51:52.670
What are you doing?

51:54.910 --> 51:56.400
- Are you going to hit me? - Yes.

51:58.500 --> 51:59.940
Did you really hit him?

52:00.210 --> 52:01.970
I almost killed him.

52:03.630 --> 52:05.180
Do you think he'll fire me?

52:05.510 --> 52:07.150
I'm the star of Haesung Hospital.

52:07.150 --> 52:09.020
But he's the Mr.Han of the hospital.

52:09.020 --> 52:09.900
Right?

52:12.720 --> 52:13.910
I need to attend the meeting.

52:13.910 --> 52:15.200
How can I face him?

52:16.850 --> 52:19.770
Give him a dirty look. Give him the dirtiest look.

52:19.770 --> 52:21.690
If you stare at him hard enough, you can hurt him.

52:23.020 --> 52:25.490
What if he falls for me even more?

52:25.490 --> 52:27.430
That's what I'm worried about.

52:27.430 --> 52:31.180
The next item in the agenda is...

52:31.180 --> 52:32.610
the medical services team to Uruk.

52:33.410 --> 52:36.560
I was thinking about taking volunteers,

52:36.560 --> 52:39.000
but I want to send our best doctors

52:39.000 --> 52:41.780
I've decided to assign Professor Kang Mo Yeon,

52:41.780 --> 52:43.240
the star of Haesung Hospital,

52:45.030 --> 52:48.530
as the leader of the medical services team.

52:48.770 --> 52:50.560
It's not a five-star hotel or anything,

52:50.560 --> 52:52.790
but you will have clean dorms.

52:53.250 --> 52:54.570
Please accept it, Professor Kang.

53:04.070 --> 53:05.890
You never know with life.

53:25.700 --> 53:27.210
Did you see the list of the medical services team?

53:29.010 --> 53:30.130
Yes, I did.

53:31.580 --> 53:34.320
The leader of the team is that doctor, right?

53:35.740 --> 53:36.820
Yes, it's her.

53:36.820 --> 53:38.630
Does she know that you're here?

53:38.970 --> 53:40.270
I don't think so.

53:41.250 --> 53:43.130
I guess you two weren't supposed to just pass by.

53:45.490 --> 53:48.200
I guess we're not just passing ships in the night.

54:03.140 --> 54:05.230
Why did you have to drag me here?

54:05.230 --> 54:08.510
They said they have send some UN solders to help us.

54:08.510 --> 54:10.280
Let's wait here.

54:10.880 --> 54:12.650
We're waiting,

54:12.650 --> 54:16.060
but it's too hot. It's freaking hot.

54:18.090 --> 54:19.820
You don't know with life.

54:21.060 --> 54:22.480
I don't know.

54:24.510 --> 54:25.660
Hello?

54:26.660 --> 54:27.970
Who's this?

54:28.740 --> 54:31.330
Chairmen? What Mr.Han?

54:31.860 --> 54:33.430
Han what?

54:34.450 --> 54:36.830
Han Suk Won?

54:36.830 --> 54:38.650
If you're Han Suk Won, you're...

54:38.650 --> 54:40.540
Why…

54:42.580 --> 54:44.510
Hello, sir.

54:44.780 --> 54:47.500
My phone didn’t connect well.

54:49.400 --> 54:53.820
Yes. We just arrived at Uruk Airport.

54:53.820 --> 54:56.620
Yes, I'll put Dr.Kang on the phone.

54:58.050 --> 55:00.240
Why didn't you answer your phone?

55:08.050 --> 55:09.460
This is Kang Mo Yeon.

55:09.460 --> 55:10.670
Isn't it hot there?

55:10.670 --> 55:12.940
If you've had a change of mind, let me know.

55:13.520 --> 55:16.280
I have so many excuses to bring you back to Korea.

55:17.900 --> 55:20.770
No, thanks.

55:20.770 --> 55:22.650
I knew you were a jerk when you lured me into a hotel room

55:22.650 --> 55:25.330
but I didn't think you'd be this low and despicable.

55:25.930 --> 55:27.640
Mr.Han,

55:29.890 --> 55:32.170
I’m telling you.

55:32.170 --> 55:33.070
Now I'm a celebrity.

55:33.070 --> 55:35.100
and have so many VIP customers.

55:35.100 --> 55:38.170
I think this is the perfect time for me to open up my own hospital.

55:38.800 --> 55:41.020
As soon as I get back to Korea,

55:41.020 --> 55:42.900
I'll throw my letter of resignation in your face.

55:42.900 --> 55:44.090
Just wait and see.

55:44.350 --> 55:45.380
Do you understand?

55:55.870 --> 55:56.870
Now you know.

55:57.790 --> 56:00.120
That's why I ended up here.

56:05.900 --> 56:07.200
Here comes the chopper.

58:18.620 --> 58:22.780
I guess we're not just passing ships in the night.

58:53.550 --> 58:56.820
Next Episode

58:57.140 --> 58:58.490
Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo's coming.

58:58.490 --> 59:00.000
Here?

59:00.310 --> 59:03.400
-Don't move! -What is it? A mine?

59:03.400 --> 59:04.890
How have you been?

59:04.890 --> 59:08.810
Are you still sexy in the OR

59:08.810 --> 59:10.790
There's been a car accident on a mountain road.

59:10.990 --> 59:13.260
Hang in there. I'll find you.

59:13.260 --> 59:18.440
I'm sorry that you were disrupted while worrying about me.

59:18.600 --> 59:21.130
FPCON2 is in effect in the Medical Zone.

59:21.130 --> 59:23.990
We should never get involved.

59:23.990 --> 59:25.140
If the patient dies...

59:25.140 --> 59:25.910
What is it?

59:25.910 --> 59:27.080
We can take it

59:27.080 --> 59:28.630
as the doctor’s fault.
